updates_from_previous_fiscal_note: The primary update is procedural and confirms the bill's status as a placeholder. Standing Committee Report 548 documents that the Senate Committee on Ways and Means has amended S.B. No. 933 by deleting its original contents and inserting language to provide unspecified, one-time grants. The bill has been recommitted to the committee for further consideration, indicating that specific appropriation amounts and details are expected to be added at a later date.
